  "files": [
    {
      "script_id": "ode",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-1",
      "filename": "intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/ode/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.12,
      "size": 18000,
      "text": "欢迎来到常微分方程实验。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "ode",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/ode/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.45,
      "size": 39168,
      "text": "你有没有想过，人口是如何增长的？放射性物质是如何衰变的？"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "ode",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/ode/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.55,
      "size": 40752,
      "text": "这些问题都涉及到变化率，而微分方程正是描述变化率的数学语言。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "ode",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-4",
      "filename": "intro-intro-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/ode/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-4.mp3",
      "duration": 1.43,
      "size": 22896,
      "text": "今天我们将探索这个强大的数学工具。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "ode",
      "section_id": "concept",
      "line_id": "concept-1",
      "filename": "concept-concept-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/ode/xiaoxiao/concept-concept-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.72,
      "size": 27504,
      "text": "微分方程是包含未知函数及其导数的方程。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "ode",
      "section_id": "concept",
      "line_id": "concept-2",
      "filename": "concept-concept-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/ode/xiaoxiao/concept-concept-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.76,
      "size": 28224,
      "text": "常微分方程只涉及一个自变量，通常是时间。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "ode",
      "section_id": "concept",
      "line_id": "concept-3",
      "filename": "concept-concept-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/ode/xiaoxiao/concept-concept-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.5,
      "size": 24048,
      "text": "解微分方程就是找到满足方程的函数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "ode",
      "section_id": "concept",
      "line_id": "concept-4",
      "filename": "concept-concept-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/ode/xiaoxiao/concept-concept-4.mp3",
      "duration": 1.42,
      "size": 22752,
      "text": "初始条件决定了众多解中的特定一个。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "ode",
      "section_id": "exponential",
      "line_id": "exp-1",
      "filename": "exponential-exp-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/ode/xiaoxiao/exponential-exp-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.84,
      "size": 29520,
      "text": "最简单的微分方程是：变化率与当前值成正比。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "ode",
      "section_id": "exponential",
      "line_id": "exp-2",
      "filename": "exponential-exp-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/ode/xiaoxiao/exponential-exp-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.93,
      "size": 30816,
      "text": "如果比例常数为正，得到指数增长，如细菌繁殖。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "ode",
      "section_id": "exponential",
      "line_id": "exp-3",
      "filename": "exponential-exp-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/ode/xiaoxiao/exponential-exp-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.05,
      "size": 32832,
      "text": "如果比例常数为负，得到指数衰减，如放射性衰变。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "ode",
      "section_id": "exponential",
      "line_id": "exp-4",
      "filename": "exponential-exp-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/ode/xiaoxiao/exponential-exp-4.mp3",
      "duration": 2.11,
      "size": 33696,
      "text": "这个方程的解是指数函数，是自然界中最常见的模式之一。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "ode",
      "section_id": "oscillation",
      "line_id": "osc-1",
      "filename": "oscillation-osc-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/ode/xiaoxiao/oscillation-osc-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.36,
      "size": 21744,
      "text": "二阶微分方程可以描述振动现象。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "ode",
      "section_id": "oscillation",
      "line_id": "osc-2",
      "filename": "oscillation-osc-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/ode/xiaoxiao/oscillation-osc-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.58,
      "size": 25344,
      "text": "简谐振动方程的解是正弦和余弦函数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "ode",
      "section_id": "oscillation",
      "line_id": "osc-3",
      "filename": "oscillation-osc-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/ode/xiaoxiao/oscillation-osc-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.29,
      "size": 20592,
      "text": "加入阻尼项，振动会逐渐衰减。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "ode",
      "section_id": "oscillation",
      "line_id": "osc-4",
      "filename": "oscillation-osc-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/ode/xiaoxiao/oscillation-osc-4.mp3",
      "duration": 1.55,
      "size": 24768,
      "text": "这个模型描述了弹簧、钟摆等周期运动。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "ode",
      "section_id": "application",
      "line_id": "app-1",
      "filename": "application-app-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/ode/xiaoxiao/application-app-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.37,
      "size": 21888,
      "text": "微分方程是科学建模的核心工具。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "ode",
      "section_id": "application",
      "line_id": "app-2",
      "filename": "application-app-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/ode/xiaoxiao/application-app-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.51,
      "size": 24192,
      "text": "物理学中的牛顿运动定律就是微分方程。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "ode",
      "section_id": "application",
      "line_id": "app-3",
      "filename": "application-app-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/ode/xiaoxiao/application-app-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.73,
      "size": 27648,
      "text": "生态学用它来模拟捕食者与猎物的动态平衡。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "ode",
      "section_id": "application",
      "line_id": "app-4",
      "filename": "application-app-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/ode/xiaoxiao/application-app-4.mp3",
      "duration": 1.34,
      "size": 21456,
      "text": "流行病学用它来预测疾病的传播。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "ode",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/ode/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.47,
      "size": 23472,
      "text": "今天我们探索了常微分方程的基本概念。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "ode",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/ode/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.73,
      "size": 27648,
      "text": "微分方程是描述变化和动态系统的数学语言。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "ode",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-3",
      "filename": "summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/ode/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.55,
      "size": 24768,
      "text": "从指数增长到周期振动，它们无处不在。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "ode",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-4",
